.DT
accept
$MUDNAME$ player help
accept

.SH Name
.SI 5
accept - Accept a sale from someone else.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
accept <name>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command is used to accept an offer of sale or inspection
from another player.  This is the safest method of selling or
buying an item, as the terms of the sale must be agreed to by
the buyer and set up by the seller, making scams harder.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> accept offer from Windy
You give 1 gold coin to Windy.
You buy a dagger from Windy.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
reject, offer, withdraw
.EI
